msg: A condition occured where sometimes the suggest list for inputSuggest was empty. This was caused by an empty <DIV> block with a choice of -1. This caused errors in the components javascript (suggest.js line 117 as of this revision). This quick fix simply skips over the erroneous Map entry and doesn't render the empty block.
